All Packages

Package Summary
Package
Description
controller.contextControllers
Package containing controller classes related to Contexts (game situations) , every context controller can update and draw his own situation.
controller.controllers
Package containing controller classes related to Controllers, that create, manage, update and draw their own related objects.
controller.filesManagers
Package containing controller classes related to Files, used to save and load files and to manage audio.
controller.inputManagers
Package containing controller classes related to Inputs, manages mouse and keyboard inputs sending them to current Context controller.
main
Package containing main class and Game class, used to initialize the game.
model.collectables
Package containing model classes related to Collectables, items that can be collected and reward you with points or power.
model.enemies
Package containing model classes related to Enemies, entities that can lower your life points when they hit you.
model.game
Package containing model classes related to game in general such as Level, Profile, Context and Entity.
model.player
Package containing model classes related to Player, the entity you can controll to move, jump and shoot bubbles.
view.userInterface
Package containing view classes related to User Interface, here you can find customized buttons and the music player.
view.window
Package containing view classes, contains a JFrame ( WindowFrame), a JPanel (GamePanel) and a customized "panel" HeadBar.
